---
title: Blue-Green and Canary Deployment Topology
---
flowchart LR
    users["Customers / UPI clients"]
    gateway["Ingress + Istio Gateway"]
    vs["Istio VirtualService<br/>weighted routing"]
    blue["Blue namespace<br/>current stable 100% or baseline"]
    green["Green namespace<br/>new release / canary 1→10→50→100%"]
    redis["Redis 7 cluster<br/>sessions + cache"]
    db["PostgreSQL 16 + pgBouncer<br/>shared backward-compatible schema"]
    prom["Prometheus + synthetic checks"]
    rollback["Rollback controller<br/>traffic re-route + verify"]
    argo["ArgoCD + Helm<br/>declarative rollout"]
    users --> gateway
    gateway --> vs
    vs -->|stable traffic| blue
    vs -->|canary/green traffic| green
    blue --> redis
    green --> redis
    blue --> db
    green --> db
    argo --> blue
    argo --> green
    prom -->|threshold breach| rollback
    rollback -->|atomic route switch| vs
    prom --> blue
    prom --> green
